http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: Jobs for Arkansas' Graduates can be utilized in any program of study and can count as credit toward a student's vocational career focus/major. The program's goal is to ensure student graduation (or GED) and prepare students for workplace success whether their career begins immediately upon high school graduation, entry into military service, or requires them to complete postsecondary education/training.
